hadiths[220]{hadithnumber,text}:
5542,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitri hain : khatna karna, sharmgaah key baal mundna, baghlon key baal ukhedna, nakhun tarashna aur munchhen chhoti karna. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney is (riwayat) ko maqoof bayan kiya hai (jaisa ke agli riwayat mein aa raha hai.)"
5543,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitrat aur sunnat hain : nakhun tarashna, munchhein kaatna, baghal key baal ukhedna, sharmgah key baal mundna aur khatna karwana."
5544,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitrat aur sunnat hain : nakhun tarashna, munchhein kaatna, baghal key baal ukhedna, sharmgah key baal mundna aur khatna karwana."
5545,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munchhon ko khatam karo aur dadhi ko badhney do.
5546,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munchhon ko khatam karo aur dadhi ko badhney do.
5547,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daadhiyaan rakho aur munchhen saaf karo.
5548,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daadhiyaan rakho aur munchhen saaf karo.
5549,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs apni munchhen na kaatey , wo hum mein sey nahin."
5550,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs apni munchhen na kaatey , wo hum mein sey nahin."
5551,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaddu key bartan, tarkol lagey huye bartan aur khajoor ki jad sey banaey gaey bartan sey mana farmaya, isi ke sath khajoor ko munaqqey sey mila kar aur pakney key qarib khajoor ko khushk khajoor sey mila kar nabeez bananey sey bhi mana farmaya."
5552,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pakney key qarib aur khushk khajoor, isi ke sath munaqqey aur khushk khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez key istemal sey mana farmaya."
5553,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khajoor aur munaqqa isi tarah pakney key qarib aur taza khajoor ko (nabeez bananey key liye) ikhatta na karo.
5554,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kachchi aur taza khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez na banao. isi tarah munaqqey aur taza khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez na banao.
5555,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khajoor aur munaqqey ya pakney key qarib aur khushk khajoor ya kachchi aur gadar khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya hai.
5556,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khajoor aur munaqqey, isi trah gadar aur taza khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez sey mana farmaya hai."
5557,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munaqqey aur khajoor isi tarah gadar aur khushk khajoor ko mila kar nabeez na banao.
5558,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney munaqqey aur khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. isi tarah gadar aur khushk khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey bhi mana farmaya.
5559,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaddu key bartan, matkey, tarkol miley huye bartan aur khajoor ki jad sey banaey gaey bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya. isi tarah gadar aur khushk khajoor ko mila kar ya munaqqey aur khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. aap ney hijr ilaaqey key logon ko likh bheja tha ke munaqqey aur khajoor ko mila kar nabeez na banao."
5560,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : basar, yani gadar khajoor akeli ki nabeez bhi haram hai aur khushk khajoor key sath mila kar bhi haram hai."
5561,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khajoor aur munaqqey aur khushk aur gadar khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez sey mana farmaya hai.
5562,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khajoor aur munaqqey ko mila kar aur khushk aur gadar khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya hai.
5563,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pakney key qarib aur taza khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez na banao. aur taza khajoor aur munaqqey ko mila kar nabeez na banao.
5564,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney munaqqey aur gadar khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. isi tarah gadar khajoor aur taza khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya.
5565,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein nabeez mein do cheezen ikhatti karney sey mana farmaya hai kyonkey eik dusri ko tez keregi. mainey un sey fazeekh key barey mein puchha to unhoney mujhey is sey mana kar diya. wo is gadar khajoor ki nabeez ko napasand kartey they jo eik taraf sey pak chuki ho, is khatrey sey ke wo do qism ka phal hai. to hum uski eik janib kaat detey they."
5566,"Hazrat Abu Idrees sey riwayat hai ke mainey dekha, Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gadar khajoor laee gaee jo eik taraf sey pak chuki thi. aap uskey pakkey huye sirey ko kaatney lagey (taake eik hissey sey nabeez banai jaey na ke dono sey)."
5567,"Hazrat Qatada ney farmaya ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) hamein eik taraf sey paki hui gadar khajoor laney ka hukm detey, phir us ka wo sira kaat diya jata."
5568,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) khajoor key pakkey huye hissey ko nahin rehney detey they balke (nabeez bananey key liye) gadar hissey sey alag kar detey they.
5569,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pakney key qarib aur paki khajuron ko mila kar nabeez na banao. (isi tarah) gadar khajoor aur munaqqey ko bhi na milaao balke in mein sey har eik ki alag alag nabeez banao.
5570,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pakney key qarib aur khushk khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez aur (isi tarah) gadar aur khushk khajoor ki mushtarka nabeez sey mana kiya. aur aap ney farmaya : in mein sey har eik ki alag alag nabeez un mishkeezon mein banao jin ka munh baandha jata hai.
5571,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney gadar (neem pukhta) khajoor ko khushk khajoor key sath mila kar ya munaqqey ko khushk khajoor key sath mila kar ya munaqqey ko gadar khajoor sey mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. aap ney farmaya : jo tum mein sey nabeez peena chahey, wo un mein sey eik chiz ki nabeez piye : sirf khushk khajoor ki ya sirf gadar khajoor ki ya sirf munaqqey ki."
5572,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney gadar khajoor ko khushk khajoor key sath ya munaqqey ko khushk khajoor key sath ya munaqqey ko gadar khajoor key sath milaaney sey mana farmaya. aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs nabeez peena chahey to in mein sey kisi eik chiz ki nabeez piye. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha ke hadees ke raawi Abu Al Muttawakil ka naam Ali bin Dawud hai.
5573,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke (nabeez bananey key liye) gadar khajoor aur munaqqey ko ya gadar aur khushk khajoor ko milaya jaey. aap ney farmaya : in mein sey har eik ki alag-alag nabeez banao.
5574,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke khajuron aur munaqqey ko mila kar ya khajuron aur gadar khajuron ko mila kar nabeez banai jaey. aap ney farmaya : munaqqey ki alag nabeez banao, khajoor ki alag aur gadar khajoor ki alag. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha ke (hadees ke raawi) Abu-Kaseer ka naam Yazid bin Abdur-Rehman hai."
5575,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sharab in do darakhton (key phalon) sey tayyar hoti hai : khajoor aur angoor.
5576,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sharab (umuman) in do darakhton (yani) khajoor aur angoor (key phalon) sey tayyar hoti hai.
5577,"Hazrat Ibrahim aur Shaabi ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz, sharab (ka hukm rakhti ) hai. (ya aayat mein) sakar sey murad sharab hai. (jo haram hai jabkey rizq hasan, yani nabeez waghera jo nasha-aawar na ho, halal hai.)"
5578,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey manqul hai (aayat mazkura mein) sakar sey murad sharab hai.
5579,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey manqul hai ke. sakar sey murad sharab hai.
5580,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber ney farmaya : sakar (nasha-aawar mashrub) haram hai. aur rizq hasan (nabeez waghera) halal hai.
5581,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madina Munawra key member par farmatey suna : aey logo ! aagah raho ! jis din sharab ki hurmat ka hukm nazil huwa, un dino sharab paanch chizon sey tayyar ki jati thi : angoor sey, khajoor sey, shehad sey, gehun sey aur jau sey aur (yaad rakho) har wo chiz sharab hai jo aql ko dhaanpey."
5582,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key member mubarak par farmatey suna : Hamd aur durud key baad (yaad rakho ke) sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to wo paanch chizon sey tayyar ki jati thi : angoor sey, gehun sey, jau sey, khajoor sey aur shehad sey."
5583,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke sharab paanch chizon sey tayyar hoti hai : khajoor sey, gehun sey, jau sey, shehad sey aur angoor sey."
5584,"Hazrat ibne Sirin sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar kaha : hamarey ghar waley Sham key waqt nabeez banatey hain. hum subah key waqt wo pi letey hain. (kya ye jayez hai?) aap ney farmaya : main tujhey nasha-aawar sey rokta hun. thoda ho ya ziyada. aur main Allah Taala ko tujh par gawah bana kar tujhey nasha-aawar chiz sey rokta hon qaleel ho ya kasir (thoda ho ziyada). aur main Allah Taala ko gawah bana kar tujhey batata hun ke khaiber waley falan falan chiz sey mashrub tayyar kartey hain aur us ka naam ye ye rakhtey hain magar wo dar-haqiqat sharab (khumr) hai. aur fidak waley bhi falan falan chiz sey mashrub tayyar kartey hain aur us ka naam ye aur ye rakhtey hain, halanke wo bhi sharab hi hai yahan tak ke unhoney chaar (qism key) mashrub shumar kiye. un mein sey eik shehad (sey tayyar hota) tha."
5585,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram aur har nasha-aawar chiz khumr hai.
5586,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai aur har nasha aawar chiz khumr hai. Husain bin Mansoor ney kaha : Imam Ahmed (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai.
5587,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz khumr (sharab) hai.
5588,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz sharab hai aur har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5589,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka farman hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai aur har nasha-aawar chiz khumr hai.
5590,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5591,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5592,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaddu key bartan, tarkol lagey huye bartan, khajoor ki jad sey banaey huye bartan aur matkey mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. aur har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai."
5593,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaddu key bartan, tarkol lagey huye bartan aur khajoor ki jad sey banaey gaey bartan mein nabeez na banao. aur har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai."
5594,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar mashrub haram hai. Quteba ney kaha : (an Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam)).
5595,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shehad ki nabeez key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : jis mashrub mein nasha paida ho jaey wo haram hai. ye alfaz Suwed key hain.
5596,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (bataa') (shehad ki sharab) key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : jis mashrub mein bhi nasha paida ho jaey wo haram ho jata hai. (bataa') (nabeez hai jo) shehad sey tayyar ki jati thi.
5597,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bitaa' key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar mashrub haram hai. bitaa' shehad ki nabeez ko kehtey hain.
5598,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5599,Hazrat Abu Burda key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aur Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen ki taraf (Mubligh aur Ameer bana kar) bheja. Hazrat Muaz ney kaha : aap hamein aisey ilaqey ki taraf bhej rahey hain jahan key log bahut qism key mashrub peetey hain. main kon sa mashrub piyun? aap ney farmaya : jo chahey pi lo magar nasha-aawar mashrub na peena.
5600,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nashey wali chiz haram hai.
5601,Hazrat Aswad bin Shebaan Sadoosi ney kaha ke Hazrat Ata sey eik aadmi ney puchha : hum lambey lambey safar kartey hain to bazaron mein hamarey samney bahut sey mashrub aatey hain. hamein ilm nahin hota ke wo kis bartan mein banaya gaya? Hazrat Ata ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar mashrub haram hai. wo dobara wohi sawal karney laga to unhoney phir farmaya : har nasha-aawar mashrub haram hai. wo phir sawal dohraaney laga to unhoney kaha : jawab wohi hai jo main tujhey dey chuka.
5602,Hazrat ibne Sirin ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz haram hai (mashrub ho ya matum).
5603,Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Tufail Jazri sey manqul hai ke Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi Alaih) (Khalifa Raashid) ney hamein likha ke tilaa na piyo yahan tak ke do tihai khushk ho kar eik tihai reh jaey aur har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5604,Hazrat Sa'aq bin Huzn sey manqul hai ke Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez ney Adi bin Irtaat ko likha ke har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5605,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nashey wali chiz haram hai.
5606,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Yamen ki taraf (Mubligh aur Ameer bana kar) bheja. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! wahan kaee qism key mashrub istimal hotey hain. main un mein sey kon sa piyun, kon sa tarak karun? aap ney farmaya : maslan : wo kon kon sey hain? mainey kaha : bitaa' aur muzar. aap ney farmaya : ye kya hotey hain? mainey kaha : bitaa' to shehad ki nabeez hoti hai aur muzar makai ki nabeez hoti hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi nasha-aawar mashrub na peena kyonkey main har nasha-aawar mashrub ko haram qarar dey chuka hun."
5607,Hazrat Abu-Barda key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Yamen ki taraf bheja to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Yamen mein kaee qism key mashrub hain jinhein bitaa' aur muzar kaha jata hai. aap ney farmaya : bitaa' aur muzar kya hain? mainey arz kiya : bitaa' to aisa mashrub hai jo shehad sey tayyar kiya jata hai aur muzar jau sey. aap ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5608,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya to sharab (ki hurmat) wali aayat padhi. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! muzar key barey mein kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : muzar kya hota hai? us ney kaha Yamen mein ghalley ki kisi qism sey tayyar kiya jata hai. aap ney farmaya : is mein nasha hota hai? us ney kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5609,"Hazrat Abul-Juweriya ney kaha : mainey suna ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya : Yaaziq key barey mein fatwaa dijiye. unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Yaziq sey pehley tashrif ley gaey aur (yaad rakho) jo chiz nasha-aawar hai, haram hai."
5610,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis mashrub ka ziyada peena nasha-aawar ho, us ko thoda peena bhi haram hai."
5611,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tumhein wo chiz maamuli si peeney sey bhi rokta hun jisey ziyada peeney sey nasha aata hai (aur kam peeney sey nasha nahin hota).
5612,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us chiz ko thoda peeney sey mana kiya hai jisey ziyada peena nasha-aawar ho.
5613,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey ilm tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney roza rakha huwa hai to mainey aap ki iftaari key liye kaddu key bartan mein nabeez tayyar kar key eik taraf rakh chhodi. phir iftaari key waqt mein wo nabeez ley kar aap key paas hazir huwa to aap ney farmaya : (merey) qarib karo. mainey wo aap key qarib ki to wo josh maar rahi thi. aap ney farmaya : isey is deewar par dey maaro. is qism ki nabeez to wo log peetey hain jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat ko nahin mantey.Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : is hadees mein daleel hai ke nasha aawar chiz qaleel (kam) bhi haram hai kasir (ziyada) bhi, na ke jaisey apney aap ko dhoka deney waley log kehtey hain ke aakhiri ghoont jis sey nasha aaya, haram hai. pehley ghoont halal hain, chahey wo eik farq pi ley, halanke ehale-ilm is baat par muttafiq hain ke nasha sirf aakhiri ghoont sey hi paida nahin hota balke pehley ghoont bhi nashey waley hi hain. Allah Taala hi tofiq deney wala hai."
5614,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey soney ki anguthi, qassi (reshmi) kapdey, surkh reshmi gadiley aur jau ki nabeez sey mana farmaya."
5615,Hazrat Sasaa ney Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! hamein us chiz sey mana farmaiye jis sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aap ko roka ho. unhonney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey kadu key bartan aur matkey (mein nabeez waghera bananey) sey mana farmaya.
5616,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye patthar key kundey mein nabeez banai jati thi.
5617,Hazrat Taoos sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney matkey ki nabeez sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. Hazrat Taoos ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! mainey ye (alfaz) un (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey suney hain.
5618,Hazrat Taoos kehtey hain ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney matkey ki nabeez sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney kaha : haan. (eik raawi) Ibrahim bin Maisraa ney apni hadees mein kadu key bartan ka bhi zikr kiya hai.
5619,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney matkey mein banai gaee nabeez key istimal sey mana farmaya hai.
5620,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (hantam) (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya hai. (Jabla bin Sahim ney kaha : ) mainey puchha ke (hantam) kya hota hai? unhoney farmaya : mitti ka matka.
5621,Hazrat Abdul-Azeez bin Usaid Taahi Basri ney farmaya Hazrat (Abdullah) ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein is sey roka tha.
5622,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke hamney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isey haram qarar diya hai. phir main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas hazir huwa aur kaha ke mainey aaj eik aisi baat suni hai jis par mujhey bahut tajjub huwa hai. unhoney kaha : wo kya baat hai? mainey kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey haram qarar diya hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney sach farmaya. mainey kaha : ji ! matkey sey kya murad hai? unhoney farmaya : mitti sey bana huwa har bartan."
5623,Hazrat Saeed Juber ney kaha ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas betha tha ke un sey matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha gaya. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isey haram qarar diya hai. mainey ye baat suni to ye mujhey bahut shaaq guzri. main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey eik masla puchha gaya to main unkey jawab par bahut hairaan huwa hun. farmaney lagey : wo kya masla tha? mainey kaha : un sey matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha gaya tha. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : unhoney sach farmaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey haram qarar diya hai. mainey kaha : matkey sey kya murad hai? unhoney farmaya : mitti sey bana huwa har bartan.
5624,Hazrat ibne Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sabz (hara) matkey ki nabeez sey mana farmaya hai. mainey kaha : safed matka (jayez hai? ) unhoney farmaya : main nahin janta.
5625,Hazrat ibne Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sabz (hara) aur safed matkey ki nabeez sey mana farmaya hai.
5626,"Hazrat Abu-Rijaa sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat Hasan Basri sey matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha : kya wo haram hai? unhoney kaha ke haram hai. mujhey us shakhs ney bayan kiya jisney jhoot nahin bola ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (roghani) matkey, kadu key bartan, tarkol lagey huye matkey aur khajoor ki jad sey banaey gaey bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya hai."
5627,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya hai.
5628,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan sey mana farmaya hai.
5629,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya hai."
5630,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye bartan (key nabeez) sey mana farmaya hai.
5631,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Ya'amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan aur tarkol miley huye bartan sey mana farmaya hai.
5632,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye bartan mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya hai.
5633,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye bartan mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya hai.
5634,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tarkol lagey huye bartan aur kadu key bartan ( mein nabeez bananey ) sey mana farmaya.
5635,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan, roghani matkey aur khajoor ki jad sey banaey gaey bartan mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya."
5636,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney roghani matkey, kadu key bartan aur khajoor ki jad sey banaey gaey bartan mein banai gaee nabeez peeney sey mana farmaya."
5637,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan, roghani matkey aur tarkol lagey huye bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya."
5638,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney matkon , kadu key bartan aur tarkol miley huye bartanon sey mana farmaya."
5639,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisa mashrub peeney sey mana farmatey suna jo kadu key bartan ya roghani matkey ya tarkol lagey huye bartan mein tayyar kiya gaya ho, ilawa zaitun key tel aur sirkey key."
5640,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan, roghani matkey, khajoor ki jad key bartan aur tarkol lagey bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya."
5641,"Hazrat Samaama bin Huzn Qusheri sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko mila to mainey un sey nabeez key barey mein puchha. unhoney farmaya : qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to unhoney aap sey puchha ke wo kis bartan mein nabeez banaeyn? Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein kadu key bartan, khajoor ki jad key bartan, tarkol lagey huye bartan aur roghani matkey mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya."
5642,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : kadu key bartan mein zaati taur par nabeez bananey sey roka gaya hai.
5643,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khajoor ki jad key bartan, tarkol lagey bartan, kadu key bartan aur roghani matkey mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. ye ibne Aleh ki riwayat mein hai. Is-haq ney kaha ke Hanida ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Muaaza ki hadees key misl (tarah) bayan kiya hai aur (khaalis) matkon ka zikr kiya. mainey Hanida sey kaha : tu ney un (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) sey suna, unhoney matkon (mitti key ghadon) ka naam liya tha? us (Hanida) ney kaha : haan."
5644,"Hazrat Hanida binte Shareek bin Aban sey manqul hai ke main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko Khareeba mein mili. mainey un sey sharab ki baqi bachi hui mail kuchail (til chhat) key barey mein puchha to unhoney mujhey is sey bhi mana kiya, is ke sath farmaya : Sham ko nabeez banao to subah ko pi liya karo. aur raat ko us ka munh baandh kar rakha karo. aur unhoney mujhey kadu key bartan, khajoor ki jad key bartan, tarkol lagey bartan aur roghani matkey sey bhi mana farmaya."
5645,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tarkol lagey huye bartanon (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya hai.
5646,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat ibne-Umar aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey suna, un dono ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par gawahi di ke aap ney kadu key bartan, roghani matkey , khajoor ki jad key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye bartan sey mana farmaya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat padhi : Rasulullah jo kuch tumhein den, wo ley lo aur jis chiz sey tumhein roken, us sey ruk jao."
5647,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid sey riwayat hai ke unkey chacha-zaad bhai Hazrat Anas sey manqul hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya Allah Taala ney (Quran Majeed mein) ye nahin farmaya : aur jo kuchh tumhein Allah ka Rasool dey, wo ley lo aur jis chiz sey rok dey, us sey ruk jao. mainey kaha : kyon nahin (balke farmaya hai). phir unhoney kaha : kya Allah Taala ney ye nahin farmaya : kisi momin mard ya momina aurat ko laaiq nahin ke jab Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool koi faisla farma den to wo apna ikhtiyar istimal kerey. mainey kaha : kyon nahin (balke farmaya hai). main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khajoor ki jad key bartan, tarkol lagey bartan, kadu key bartan aur roghani matkey sey mana farmaya hai."
5648,"Hazrat Azan sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey guzarish ki ke mujhey koi aisi chiz bayan farmaiye jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey un bartanon key barey mein suni ho. uski wazahat bhi farmaiye. unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (hantam) sey mana farmaya aur isey tum matka kehtey ho. aur dabaa sey mana farmaya, jisey tum kadu ka bartan kehtey ho. aur naqeer sey mana farmaya. ye khajoor ki jad hoti hai jisey log andar sey kured kured kar bartan bana letey hain, neez aap ney muzaffat sey mana farmaya aur ye wo bartan hota hai jisey tarkol ya lakh mal di gaee ho."
5649,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap ney in ko kadu key bartan, khajoor ki jad key bartan, tarkol lagey bartan aur katey huye munh waley mishkeezey mein nabeez bananey sey rok diya aur farmaya : apney (maroof) mishkeezey mein nabeez banao aur us ka munh baandh kar rakho aur usey meethi meethi piyo. eik shakhs ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey us jaisi (mutghaiyar (juda)) nabeez peeney ki bhi ijazat dey dijiye. aap ney farmaya : phir to to usey aisi (nashey wali) bana lega. aap ney usey bayan karney key liye haath sey ishara bhi farmaya."
5650,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tarkol lagey huye matkey, kadu key bartan aur khajoor ki jad key bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya hai. aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko nabeez bananey key liye mishkeeza na milta to pathar key kundey mein aap key liye nabeez banai jati thi."
5651,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye chamdey key mishkeezey mein nabeez banai jati thi aur jab mishkeeza muyassar na hota to pathar key kundey mein aap key liye nabeez banai jati. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan, khajoor ki jad key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye matkey sey mana farmaya hai."
5652,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan, khajoor ki jad key bartan, (roghani) matkey aur tarkol lagey huye bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya."
5653,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey matkey mein nabeez bananey ki ijazat di hai jis ko tarkol (ya raughan) na lagaya gaya ho.
5654,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein (teen din sey zayed) qurbaaniyon key gosht (khaney) sey mana farmaya tha. ab (tumhein ijazat hai) safar mein sath ley kar jao ya mehfooz kar key rakho. isi tarah jo shakhs qabron ki ziyaarat ko jana chahey, wo ja sakta hai kyonkey wo aakhirat ki yad dilaati hain. isi tarah (jis bartan ki nabeez chaho) piyo lekin har nasha-aawar mashrub sey bacho."
5655,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein qabron ki ziyaarat sey roka tha. ab tum ziyaarat ko ja saktey ho. mainey tumhein teen din sey zayed qurbani key gosht (khaney) sey roka tha, ab tum jab tak chaho, rakh saktey ho. aur mainey tumhein mishkeezey key ilawa dusrey bartanon mein nabeez bananey sey roka tha, ab tum sab bartanon mein (nabeez bana kar) pi saktey ho lekin nasha-aawar mashrub na peena."
5656,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein teen chizon sey roka tha : qabron ki ziyaarat sey. ab tum ziyaarat kiya karo kyonkey ummid hai qabron ki ziyaarat tumhari neki mein izaafey ka baais hogi. (ya lekin qabron ki ziyaarat sey tumhari neki mein izafa hona chahiye.) mainey tumhein teen din sey zayed qurbani key gosht (khaney) sey roka tha. ab jab tak chaho khao. aur mainey tumhein chand bartanon mein nabeez waghera bananey sey roka tha, ab tum jis bartan mein chaho, banao aur piyo lekin nasha-aawar mashrub na piyo."
5657,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein baaz bartanon (mein nabeez bananey) sey roka tha. ab jis bartan mein chaho, nabeez banao lekin har nasha-aawar chiz sey bacho."
5658,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) safar farma rahey they ke eik qom key yahan thehrey. aap ney un mein shor aur ghul suna to farmaya : ye kaisi aawaz hai? logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! wo eik qism ka mashrub pi rahey hain. aap ney in ko pegham bhej kar bulaya aur farmaya : tum kis chiz mein nabeez banatey ho? unhoney kaha : hum khajoor ki jad key bartan aur kadu key bartan mein nabeez banatey hain. hamarey paas koi aur bartan nahin hain. aap ney farmaya : sirf aisey bartan sey piyo (aisey bartan mein nabeez banao) jis ka munh tasmey sey baandh sako. is baat ko kuchh arsa guzra jis qadr Allah Taala ney chaha, phir aap dobara us qom key paas gaey to dekha ke in ko bimari laahiq ho chuki hai aur wo zard ho chukey hain. aap ney farmaya : tumhein kya huwa hai, tum to qaribul-maut nazar aatey ho? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! hamara ilaaqa wabaa wala hai jabkey aap ney hum par mishkeezey ki nabeez key ilawa har nabeez haram farma di thi. aap ney farmaya : (jis bartan mein chaho bana kar) piyo lekin har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai."
5659,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney baaz bartanon key istimal sey rok diya to Ansaar ney narmi se kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey paas aur bartan (ziyada tadaad mein) nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir koi harj nahin.
5660,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj par ley jaya gaya to aap ko do piyaley pesh kiye gaey. eik mein doodh tha aur dusrey mein sharab. aap ney un dono ko dekha. phir doodh (wala piyala) pakad liya. Hazrat Jibril alehissalam ney aap sey farmaya : Allah Taala ka shukr hai ke us ney aap ko fitri chiz ikhtiyar karney ki tofiq ata farmaai. agar aap sharab qubul kar letey to aap ki ummat (majmui taur par) gumrah ho jati."
5661,Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuchh log sharab piyengey magar us ka naam kuchh aur rakh leingey.
5662,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab zina karney wala zina karta hai to wo momin nahin rehta. jab sharab peeney wala sharab peeta hai to wo momin nahin rehta. jab chor chori karta hai to wo momin nahin rehta. aur jab koi shakhs daaka daalta hai ke log dehshat sey dekhtey reh jatey hain to wo momin nahin rehta.
5663,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zaani zina kartey waqt momin nahin rehta. chor chori kartey waqt momin nahin rehta. shraabi sharab peetey waqt momin nahin rehta. aur daaku azimushshan daaka maartay waqt ke musalman uski taraf dekhtey hi reh jaeyn, momin nahin rehta."
5664,"Hazrat ibne-Umar aur sahaba Rizwaanllahi alaihim ajmaeen ki eik jamaat sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sharab piye, usey kodey lagao. phir sharab piye to phir kodey lagao. phir pi ley to phir kodey lagao. aur agar (chauthi dafa) phir pi bethey to usey qatl kar do."
5665,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs nasha karey to usey kodey lagao, phir nasha karey to phir kodey lagao, phir nasha karey to phir bhi kodey lagao. agar chauthi dafa nasha karey to uski gardan utaar do."
5666,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : mujhey koi parwa nahin ke main sharab piyun ya Allah Taala ko chhod kar us sutoon ki ibadat karun.
5667,"Hazrat ibne Dailmi (ghodey par) sawar Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ko talash kar rahey they. unhoney kaha ke main unkey paas pahuncha to mainey kaha : aey Abdullah bin Amr ! kya aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko sharab ki baabat kuchh bayan farmatey suna hai? unhoney kaha : han, mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : meri ummat mein sey jo shakhs sharab piye ga , Allah Taala chaalis din tak uski namaz qubul nahin farmaeyga."
5668,"Hazrat Masruq ney kaha ke jab Qazi tohfa wasul karey to us ney haram khaya aur jab rishwat qubul kar ley to ye us ko kufr tak pahuncha deti hai. aur Masruq ney (ye bhi) kaha ke jis shakhs ney sharab pi, us ney kufr kiya. aur us ka kufr ye hai ke uski namaz qubul nahin hoti."
5669,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Haris sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna : sharab sey bacho. ye tamam kharabiyon aur gunahon ki jad hai. tum sey pehley logon main eik bahut bada abid shakhs tha. eik bad-kar aurat uskey peechhey pad gaee (aur usey phasana chaha). us ney apni londi ko abid ki taraf bheja aur kaha ke hum aap ko eik gawahi key silsiley mein bulana chahtey hain. wo abid londi key sath chal pada. jab wo kisi darwazey mein dakhil ho jata to wo peechhey sey band kar deti (aur taala laga deti) yahan tak ke wo eik khoobsurat aurat key paas pahunch gaya jis key paas eik ladka tha aur eik sharab ka matka. wo aurat kehney lagi : Allah ki qism ! mainey aap ko kisi gawahi key liye nahin bulaya balke mainey to is liye bulaya hai ke aap mujh sey bad-kari karen ya ye sharab pi lein ya phir is ladkey ko qatl kar den. us abid ney (soch kar) kaha : mujhey us sharab ka eik glass pila dey. us ney usey sharab ka eik glass pila diya. wo (nashey mein aa kar) kehney laga : mujhey aur pilao. wo peeta raha yahan tak ke us ney us aurat key sath bad-kari bhi kar li aur us ladkey ko bhi maar diya, lihaza sharab sey bacho. Allah ki qism ! sharab par hameshgi aur dawaam aur eman ikhattey nahin hongey magar un mein sey eik dusrey ko nikal dega."
5670,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Haris sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna : sharab sey door raho kyonkey ye tamam buraiyon ki jad hai. tum sey pehley logon main eik bada abid shakhs tha. wo logon sey alag thalag rehta tha. (phir raawi ney saabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan ki) phir farmaya : sharab sey door raho. Allah ki qism ! sharab aur eman kisi shakhs mein ikhattey nahin hongey magar un mein sey koi eik dusrey ko nikal bahar kerega.
5671,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis shakhs ney sharab pi lekin wo nashey mein madhosh na huwa to jab tak wo sharab zarra bhar bhi uskey pet ya ragon mein rahegi to uski namaz qubul nahin hogi. aur agar wo is haal mein mar gaya to kafir ki maut mareyga. aur agar wo nashey mein badmast ho gaya to chaalis din tak uski namaz qubul na hogi. aur agar is doran mein mar gaya to kafir ki maut mareyga. Yazid bin Abu Ziyad ney is (Fuzail) ki mukhalifat ki hai."
5672,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sharab piye aur usey apney pet mein daley, Allah Taala saat din tak uski namaz qubul nahin farmata. agar wo in saat dino mein mar gaya to kafir ki maut mareyga. aur agar sharab ney uski aql maar di aur wo kisi qur'aani fareezey key tarak ka murtakib ho gaya to chaalis din tak uski namaz qubul nahin hogi. aur agar wo is doran mein mar gaya to kafir ki maut mareyga."
5673,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Dailmi sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas hazir huwa to wo Taaif mein apney eik baagh mein they jisey vahat kaha jata tha. wo us waqt eik quraishi nojawan key haath mein haath daley huye ja rahey they. us nojawan key barey mein mashhoor tha ke wo shraabi hai. wo farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jis shakhs ney eik dafa sharab pi, chaalis din tak uski namaz qubul nahin hogi. phir agar wo tauba karey to Allah Taala uski tauba qubul farma lega.  agar dobara piye to phir chaalis din tak uski namaz qubul nahin hogi. agar phir bhi tauba karey to Allah Taala uski tauba qubul farma lega. lekin agar phir pi ley to Allah Taala ney qism kha rakhi hai ke qiyamat key din zarur usey jahannamiyon ki peep palaeyga. (hadees key) ye lafz Amr key hain."
5674,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs duniya mein sharab piyega aur is sey tauba nahin kerega, wo aakhirat mein jannati sharab sey mehroom rahega."
5675,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ehsan jatlaaney wala, maa baap ka nafarman aur sharab noshi ka aadi jannat mein nahin jaeyngey."
5676,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs duniya mein sharab peeta aur martey dum tak us ka aadi raha, us sey tauba nahin ki, wo aakhirat mein jannati sharab nahin pi sakeyga."
5677,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs duniya mein sharab piye aur maut tak peeta rahey (tauba na kerey) wo aakhirat mein jannati sharab nahin piyega.
5678,"Hazrat Suhak ney farmaya : jo shakhs sharab ka aadi raha aur usi haal mein mar gaya, jab wo duniya sey rukhsat hoga to uskey chehrey par garm pani dala jaeyga."
5679,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rabeea bin Umayya ko sharab peeney ki bina par khaibar ki taraf jala watan kar diya tha magar wo (Romi badshah) Hiraql key yahan chala gaya aur Esai ban gaya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aaj key baad mein kisi musalman ko jala watan nahin karunga."
5680,Hazrat Abu-Barda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tamam bartanon mein bana huwa mashrub tum pi saktey ho lekin tum nashey mein na aana. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha ke ye hadees munkir hai. Abul-Ehwas Salam bin Sulaim ney is mein ghalati ki hai. Simaak bin Harab key as-haab (shagirdon) main sey kisi ney bhi iski mutaabiat nahin ki jabkey (khud) Simaak qawi nahin. aur wo talqin qubul karta tha (jis tarah koi kehta usey maan leta aur apni riwayat isi tarah badal leta tha). Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya ke Abul-Ehwas is hadees mein ghalati kiya karta tha. is hadees ki sanad aur iskey alfaz mein Shareek ney uski mukhalifat ki hai.
5681,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kadu key bartan, raughani matkey, khajoor ki jad key bartan aur tarkol lagey huye bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya. Abu-Awaana ney us (Shareek raawi hadees) ki mukhalifat ki hai."
5682,Qasaafa naami eik aurat sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : har mashrub pi saktey ho magar nashay mein na aao. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya ke ye riwayat bhi sahih nahin kyonkey hum (muhaddeseen) nahin jantey ye Qarsaafa kon aur kaisi aurat hai? jab ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey mashhoor riwayaat iskey khilaf hain jo un sey Qasaafa ney bayan kiya hai.
5683,"Hazrat Jasraa binte Dajaaja Aamiriya ney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey kuchh logon ney masaayel puchhey. taqriban sab log un sey nabeez key barey mein poochh rahey they ke hum subah key waqt khajuron ko bhigotey (nabeez banatey) hain, Sham ko pi letey hain aur Sham ko bhigotey (nabeez banatey) hain to subah ko pi letey hain. to mainey in ko farmatey suna : main kisi nasha-aawar chiz ko halal nahin keh sakti, chahey wo roti ho, chahey wo pani ho. unhoney teen dafa farmaya."
5684,"Hazrat Kareema binte Hamaam sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko farmatey suna : tumhein kadu key bartan sey roka gaya hai, tumhein raughani matkey (ki nabeez) sey mana kiya gaya hai, tumhein tarkol waley bartan (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana kiya gaya hai. phir aap aurton ki taraf mutawajjeh huin aur farmaya : sabz (hara) raughani matkey (ki nabeez) sey bacho. agar tumharey matkey ka pani bhi nasha dey to usey na piyo (na pilao)."
5685,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey kuchh mashrubat key barey mein sawal kiya gaya to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har nasha-aawar chiz sey mana farmatey they. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney kaha ke) un logon ney Abdullah bin Shaddad ki Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan karda riwayat sey daleel pakdi hai.
5686,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke khumr (sharab) to qaleel bhi haram hai aur kasir bhi jabkey dusrey mashrubat sey nasha-aawar (haram hain). ibne Shabarma ney ye hadees Abdullah bin Shaddad sey nahin suni.
5687,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : sharab bilkul wesey hi haram hai, thodi ho ya ziyada. aur har dusrey mashrub sey nasha (haram hai). Abu Aun Muhammad bin Ubedullah Saqafi ney us (ibne Shabarma) ki mukhalifat ki hai (jaisa ke aainda riwayat sey zahir ho raha hai)."
5688,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : sharab bilkul wesey hi haram hai, qaleel ho ya kasir, isi ke sath har nasha-aawar mashrub bhi haram hai. ibne hukm ney (قلیلہا و کثیرھا) key alfaz bayan nahin kiye."
5689,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : sharab qaleel ho ya kasir haram hai. isi tarah har nasha-aawar mashrub bhi. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha ke ye riwayat ibne Shabarma ki (bayan karda) riwayat sey ziyada durust hai. Hasheem bin Bashir Tadlees karta tha aur uski hadees mein is (Hasheem) key ibne Shabarma sey sun'ney ka zikr bhi nahin. aur Abu-Aaun ki riwayat, Siqaat ki Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan karda riwayat key bahut mushabeh (jaisi) hai."
5690,Hazrat Abul Juweriya Jurmi sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Kaba Shareef sey tek lagaey bethey they ke mainey un sey Yaaziq key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Yaaziq (sharab) sey pehley tashrif ley gaey (lekin aap ka farman mojud hai ke) har nasha-aawar mashrub haram hai. Abul Juweriya ney kaha ke main pehla Arbi tha jisney un sey yaaziq key barey mein puchha.
5691,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jo shakhs pasand karta hai ke Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki haram karda ashiya (cheezon) ko haram kahe to wo (nasha-aawar) nabeez ko haram qarar dey.
5692,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke main khuraasaan ke ilaaqey sey talluq rakhta hun. hamara ilaaqa sakht thanda hai. (sardi ka tod karney key liye) hum munaqqaa aur angoor waghera sey mashrub tayyar kartey hain jisey hum peetey hain. mujhey uski (hillat aur hurmat) key barey mein shubeh hai. phir us ney aur kaee qism key mashrub bhi zikr kiye yahan tak ke mainey khayal kiya ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein nahin samjha. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tu ney badi lambi chodi baaten ki hain. (zaabte ki baat yad rakh ke) har nasha-aawar chiz sey ijtinab kar (bachta reh), chahey wo khajoor sey tayyar ho ya munaqqaa sey ya kisi aur phal sey."
5693,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : gadar khajoor ki nabeez haram hai, hargiz halal nahin."
5694,"Hazrat Abu-Jamra ney kaha ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur logon (sawal karnewaley) key darmiyan tarjamaani ka fariza sar-anjaam diya karta tha. eik aurat unkey paas aai aur matkey ki nabeez key barey mein poochhney lagi. unhoney us sey mana farmaya. mainey kaha : aey Abu-Abbaas ! main sabz (hara) raughani matkey mein meethi nabeez banata hun, phir is mein sey peeta hun to merey pet mein gadh-gadh hoti hai. unhoney kaha ke aisi nabeez mat pi, agar-che wo shehad sey ziyada meethi ho."
5695,"Hazrat Abu-Jamra Nasar ney bayan kiya ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke meri daadi merey liye eik matkey mein nabeez banati hain. main usey peeta hun to wo bilkul meethi hoti hai lekin agar main usey ziyada miqdaar mein pi lun, phir logon mein ja bethun to mujhey khatra hota hai ke main (koi namunasib baat kar key) kahin ruswa na ho jaun. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap ney farmaya : khush aamadeed us wafad ko jo na ruswa huye na naadim. wo kehney lagey : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey aur aap key darmiyan mushrekin haael (rukaawat) hain. hum hurmat key mahinon key ilawa aap tak nahin pahunch saktey, lihaza hamein koi aisi Jaamey baat bayan farmaain jis par amal kar key hum jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyn aur hum uski taraf logon ko bhi dawat den. aap ney farmaya : main tumhein teen chizon ka hukm deta hun aur chaar chizon sey rokta hun : main tumhein Allah Taala par eman laney ka hukm deta hun. kya tum jantey ho ke Allah Taala par eman laney ka kya matlab hai? unhoney kaha : Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hi khub jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin, namaz qaaim karna, Zakat ada karna aur ye ke tum ghanimat sey khums (paanchwan hissa) hukumat ko do. aur main tumhein chaar chizon sey mana karta hun : is nabeez sey jo kadu key bartan, khajoor ki jad key bartan, raughani matkey aur tarkol lagey huye bartan mein banai jaey."
5696,(thodi sharab ko jayez kehney waley) un logon ney Abdul-Malik bin Naafey ki Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi riwayat (5697) sey bhi daleel di hai.
5697,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey dekha ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik piyala ley kar aaya. is mein nabeez thi jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us waqt rukn key paas they. us ney piyala aap ko pakda diya. aap ney usey apney munh mubarak ki taraf badhaaya to aap ney usey talkh mehsus kiya aur usey wapis kar diya. logon mein sey eik aadmi ney aap sey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya ye haram hai? aap ney farmaya : is (piyaley waley) aadmi ko wapis merey paas lao. usey laya gaya to aap ney us sey piyala pakda. phir kuchh pani mangwakar is mein dala. phir usey apney munh mubarak ki taraf badhaya lekin phir teori si chadhai. phir aur pani mangwaya aur is mein dala. phir farmaya : jab un bartanon ki nabeez mein nasha aur talkhi paida honey lagey to uski tezi ko pani sey tod liya karo.
5698,(eik dusri sanad sey) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey aisi hi riwayat naqal farmaee hai. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha ke is riwayat ka raawi Abdul Malik bin Naafey mashhoor nahin aur na uski hadees qabile aehtijaaj hai jab ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul mashhoor riwayaat is riwayat key khilaf hain.
5699,Hazrat Zaid bin Juber (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey chand mashrubat key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : har josh waley mashrub sey perhez karo.
5700,Hazrat Zaid bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey chand mashrubat key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : har nasha-aawar mashrub sey door raho.
5701,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : nasha-aawar chiz thodi bhi haram hai aur ziyada bhi.
5702,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz sharab hai. aur har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5703,Hazrat Abdullah (ibne-Umar) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney sharab ko haram qarar diya hai aur (yaad rakho) har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5704,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai aur har nasha-aawar mashrub sharab hai. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha ke ye log (in chhe riwayaat key raawi) intehai qabile-aetbar aur qabile-bharosa aur aadil hain aur wo sahih riwayaat bayan karney mein mashhoor hain jabkey Abdul-Malik bin Naafey (jawaz wali riwayat ka raawi) kisi bhi lihaz sey in mein sey kisi eik ka bhi hum palla nahin, chahey (chahey) is jaisey kaee raawi iskey sath mil jaeyn (وباللہ التوفیقّ)."
5705,Hazrat Ruqaiya binte Amr bin Saeed ney bayan kiya ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar parwarish pai hai. aap key liye munaqqa pani mein dala jata. aap agli subah is pani ko pi letey aur munaqqey ko khushk kar liya jata. phir in mein aur munaqqa mila kar mazeed pani dal diya jata. isey aap agley din pi letey. iskey baad is munaqqey ko phenk detey. isi tarah un logon ney Hazrat Abu-Masood Aqba bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aainda riwayaat sey bhi istidlaal kiya (daleel di) hai.
5706,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Kaba mushrifa ka tawaf kartey huye piyas lag gaee. aap ney pani manga to aap key paas mishkeezey mein sey nabeez laee gaee. aap ney usey soonghaa to teori chadhai aur farmaya : merey paas zamzam key pani ka eik dol lao. phir aap ney wo pani is mein dala aur nosh farma liya. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya ye haram hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin. aur (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney) farmaya ye hadees bhi zaeef hai kyonkey Hazrat Sufiyan Sauri key shagirdon mein sey sirf Yahya bin yamaan hi is ko bayan karta hai. lekin us ka haafiza kharab tha aur wo bahut ghaltiyaan karta tha, isliye uski bayan karda riwayat qabile hujjat nahin."
5707,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mujhey ilm tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) un dino rozey rakha kartey hain, isliye mainey kadu key bartan mein nabeez bana kar aap ki iftaari key liye alag rakh chhodi. jab Sham hui to main usey uthaey aap key paas hazir huwa aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey ilm tha ke aaj aap rozey sey hain to mainey ye nabeez aap ki iftaari key liye rakhi hui thi. aap ney farmaya : aey Abu-Hurera ! ye merey paas lao. mainey wo aap ko pesh ki to wo ubal rahi thi. aap ney farmaya : isey pakdo aur deewar par dey maar. ye to un logon ka mashrub hai jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat par eman nahin rakhtey. un logon ney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key ( aainda mazkur) fe'l (kaam) sey bhi istidlaal kiya (daleel di) hai."
5708,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab tumhein nabeez mein tezi aur josh ka khatra ho to uski tezi ko pani sey tod liya karo. (raawi hadees) Abdullah ney kaha : (yani) uski tezi sey pehley (pani milaao. tezi key baad nahin kyonkey phir to nasha paida ho chuka).
5709,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke Banu Saqif ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik mashrub pesh kiya. aap ney mangwakar jab usey apney munh key qarib kiya to usey napasand farmaya. phir pani mila kar uski tezi todi aur farmaya : is qism key mashrub ko aisey kar liya karo.
5710,"Hazrat Aqba bin Farqad sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke jo nabeez Hazrat umr bin Khattab nosh farmaya kartey they wo sirke ki tarah tursh hota tha. is riwayat ki sehat par Hazrat Saaib ki aainda riwayat bhi dalalat karti hai."
5711,Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid ney bayan farmaya ke eik dafa Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya ke mainey falan shakhs sey sharab ki boo mehsus ki hai lekin wo kehta hai ke ye tilaa ki sharab hai. main iskey barey mein poochh-gachh karunga. agar wo tilaa nasha-aawar sabit huwa to main is par had lagaaunga. phir (tehqiq key baad) Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney is par puri had lagai.
5712,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik aadmi Jishaan sey aaya, aur Jishaan Yamen mein hai, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochhney laga ke hamarey ilaqey mein log eik mashrub peetey hain jo wo chini sey tayyar kartey hain. usey muzir kaha jata hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney puchha : kya wo nasha-aawar hota hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai. yaqinan Allah Taala ney qism kha rakhi hai ke jo shakhs nasha-aawar mashrub piyega, Allah Taala usey (tintul-khabal) pilaeyga. logon ney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (tintul-khabal) kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : jahannamiyon ka paseena ya farmaya : jahannamiyon ka khoon aur peep (jo unkey zakhmon sey nikleyga)."
5713,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : be-shak halal wazeh hai, haram wazeh hai aur kuchh cheezen inke beech shubeh wali hain. main iski eik misal bayan karta hun. Allah Taala ney eik ilaaqa mamnoo qarar diya (mana kiya hua) hai. aur Allah Taala ka mamnoo ilaaqa uski haram karda cheezen hain. jo shakhs us mamnoo ilaqey key ird-gird janwer charaaeyga, khatra rahega ke wo mamnoo charaagaah mein ja padingey. isi tarah jo shakhs shubeh waley kamon mein padeyga, bahut mumkin hai ke haram par bhi jurat kar ley."
5714,"Hazrat Abul-Hora Sa'di sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey koi farman yad rakha hai? unhoney kaha ke mainey aap ka ye farman yad rakha hai : mashkook aur shubeh wali chiz ko chhod kar wo chiz ikhtiyar karo jo shubeh mein na ho."
5715,Hazrat Taoos napasand farmatey they ke us shakhs ko munaqqa bechaa jaey jo us sey nasha-aawar mashrub tayyar karta hai.
5716,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke (walid mohtaram) Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki milkiyat mein angoor ki bahut si bailen aur darkht they. wahan unhoney eik shakhs ko bator zimme-daar nazim rakha huwa tha. eik saal bahut phal laga. nazim ney unko likha : mujhey khatra hai angoor zaya ho jaeyngey. agar aap ijazat den to hum inka joos nikal lein. Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey jawab mein likha : jab mera ye khat terey paas pahunchey to meri zamin sey nikal jana. Allah ki qism ! aaj key baad main tujhey kisi maamuli si chiz ka zimmedaar bhi nahin banaunga. aur haqiqat mein unhoney usey apni zamin sey hata diya."
5717,"Hazrat ibne Sirin sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke to angooron ka joos us shakhs ko bech sakta hai jo is sey tilaa banaey, sharab na banaey."
5718,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney eik governer ko likha ke musalmanon ko wo tilaa peeney do jis mein do tihai joos khushk ho chuka ho aur eik tihai baqi reh gaya ho.
5719,"Hazrat Aamir bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha huwa khat padha : hamd aur darood key baad ! merey paas Sham sey eik tijarati qafila aaya hai jinkey paas siyah rang ka eik gaadhaa sa mashrub hai, jaisey oonton ko milney wali gandhak hoti hai. mainey un sey puchha ke tum isey kis tarah pakaatey ho? unhoney mujhey bataya ke hum isey do tihai khushk honey tak pakaatey hain. is tarah uskey do khabees ajza (parts) khatam ho jatey hain, yani iska nasha aur iski boo. (aur baqi khalis aur pak mithaas reh jati hai.) lihaza tum apney ilaqey key logon ko aisa mashrub peeney do."
5720,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazid Khutmi sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney hum ko likha : hamd aur durud key baad ! tum angoor key joos ko itna pakaao ke is mein sey shetan ka hissa khatam ho jaey. do hissey uskey hain, eik hissa tumhara hai."
5721,"Hazrat Shaabi sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko wo tilaa peeney detey they jis mein agar makkhi gir jati to nikal nahin sakti thi."
5722,"Hazrat Dawud sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey puchha, wo kon sa mashrub tha jisey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney halal qarar diya tha? unhoney farmaya : jisey itna pakaayaa jaey ke wo do tihai khushk ho jaey aur eik tihai reh jaey."
5723,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ney farmaya : Hazrat Abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) wo tilaa peetey they jis mein sey do tihai khushk ho chuka hota aur eik tihai baqi reh gaya hota.
5724,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke wo aisa tilaa piya kartey they jis mein sey do tihai khushk ho chuka hota aur eik tihai baqi reh gaya hota.
5725,Hazrat Yaala bin Ata sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) ney Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey us mashrub key barey mein puchha jo nisf khushk ho chuka ho? to mainey in ko farmatey suna : nahin yahan tak ke do tihai khushk ho jaey aur eik tihai baqi reh jaey.
5726,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ney farmaya : jab tilaa is tarah pakaayaa gaya ho ke eik tihai reh jaey to usey istimal karney mein koi harj nahin.
5727,Hazrat Abu-Rijaa ney farmaya ke mainey Hazrat Hasan Basri sey us tiley key barey mein puchha jis mein sey nisf (aadha) khushk ho chuka ho? to unhoney farmaya : usey mat pi.
5728,Hazrat Bashir bin Muhaajir ney farmaya ke mainey Hazrat Hasan Basri sey angooron key pakkey huye joos key barey mein puchha ke kon sa jayez hai? unhoney farmaya : jisey itna pakaayaa jaey ke wo do tihai khushk ho jaey aur eik tihai baqi reh jaey.
5729,Hazrat Anas bin Sirin sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke Hazrat Nuh alehissalam sey shetan ney angoor ki bail key barey mein jhagda kiya. unhoney farmaya : ye meri hai. shetan ney kaha : ye meri hai. aakhir dono ney is baat par suleh kar li ke eik tihai Hazrat Nuh alehissalam ki hogi aur do tihai shetan ki.
5730,Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Tufail Jazri sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney hamein likha ke tilaa na piyo yahan tak ke is mein sey do tihai khushk ho jaey aur eik tihai baqi reh jaey. aur (yaad rakho) har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai (chahey wo tilaa hi ho).
5731,Hazrat Makhool ney kaha ke har nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.
5732,"Hazrat Abu Sabit Sa'albi sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas mojud tha ke eik aadmi aaya aur un sey angooron key joos key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : jab tak wo taza ho, tum pi saktey ho. us ney kaha ke mainey eik mashrub ko aag par pakaayaa hai lekin mujhey uskey barey mein itminan nahin. unhoney farmaya : kya us ko pakaaney sey pehley to usey pi sakta tha? us ney kaha : nahin. unhoney farmaya : phir aag to kisi haram chiz ko halal nahin kar sakti."
5733,"Hazrat Ata ney bataya ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna : Allah ki qism ! aag na kisi chiz ko halal kar sakti hai na haram. phir Hazrat Ata ney is qol ki tafseer bayan ki ke log kehtey hain, nasha-aawar mashrub ko aag par pakka kar tilaa bana liya jaey to wo halal ho jata hai (halanke ye mumkin nahin). aag kisi chiz ko halal nahin kar sakti. isi tarah haram bhi nahin kar sakti. jis tarah aag sey paki hui chiz sey wuzu karney ka masla hai."
5734,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ney farmaya ke angooron ka joos us waqt tak pi saktey ho jab tak is mein jhaag paida na ho.
5735,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aaid Asadi sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Ibrahim (Nakhai) sey angooron key joos key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : jab tak is mein josh aur badlaaw samney na aaya to, to isey pi sakta hai."
5736,Hazrat Ata ney angooron key joos key barey mein farmaya : josh aur jhaag paida honey sey pehley isey pi saktey ho.
5737,Hazrat Shaabi ney farmaya : joos ko teen din tak bhi piya ja sakta hai ba-sharte-ke is mein josh aur jhaag paida na ho.
5738,"Hazrat Feeroz Dailmi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey ilaqey mein angoor bahut hota hai jabkey Allah Taala ney sharab ki hurmat ka hukm nazil farma diya hai. hum kya keren? aap ney farmaya : tum usey munaqqa bana lo. mainey arz kiya : munaqqey ka hum kya keren? aap ney farmaya : tum subah key waqt isey pani mein bhigo diya karo aur Sham key waqt pi liya karo. isi tarah Sham key waqt usey bhigo diya karo aur subah key waqt pi liya karo. mainey kaha : hum us ko ziyada der tak na pada rehney den ke wo gaadhaa ho jaey? aap ney farmaya : matkon mein dal kar na rakho balke chamdey key mishkeezon mein rakho kyonkey un mein ziyada der bhi pada raha to sirka ban jaeyga."
5739,"Hazrat Dailmi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey yahan angoor bahut hotey hain, hum unka kya keren? aap ney farmaya : unka munaqqa bana lo. hamney kaha : phir munaqqey ka kya keren? aap ney farmaya : subah key waqt nabeez bana liya karo aur Sham key khaney key sath pi liya karo. isi tarah Sham key waqt nabeez bana subah key khaney key sath pi liya karo. lekin nabeez chamdey key mishkeezon mein banao. matkon mein na banao kyonkey mishkeezon mein agar wo der tak bhi pada raha to wo sirka ban jaeyga."
5740,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye nabeez banaya jata tha. aap usey agley din ya is sey agley din pi letey they. jab teesri raat ki Sham ho jati to agar bartan mein kuchh bacha rehta jo abhi tak piya na ja saka hota to usey baha diya jata.
5741,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye munaqqa pani mein bhigoya jata to aap isey is din, agley din aur us sey agley din pi liya kartey they."
5742,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye munaqqey ki nabeez raat ko banai jati. aap isey mishkeezey mein banatey. phir us din, agley din aur us sey agley din tak usey peetey rehtey. jab teesri raat hoti to usey pi letey ya kisi ko pila detey aur agar subh tak kuch bachi rehti to usey baha detey."
5743,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey mutalliq riwayat hai ke unkey liye subah key waqt mishkeezey mein munaqqa bhigoya jata to wo usey raat ko pi letey aur Sham key waqt bhigoya jata to din ko pi letey. aap mishkeezon ko achchhi tarah dhoya kartey they aur talchat waghera koi chiz is mein nahin daltey they. Hazrat Naafey (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) key Mola aur shagrid) ney farmaya ke hum us nabeez ko peetey they to wo shehad jaisi hoti thi.
5744,Hazrat Basam sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Abu-Jafar (Baaqar) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey nabeez key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : walid (mohtaram) Hazrat Ali bin Husain (Zainul-Aabdeen) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key liye raat key waqt nabeez banai jati to usey din ko pi letey aur din key waqt banai jati to raat ko pi letey.
5745,Hazrat Abdullah (bin mubarak) ney farmaya ke Hazrat Sufiyan (Sauri) sey nabeez key barey mein puchha gaya to mainey unhein farmatey suna ke raat ko nabeez bana aur subah pi ley.
5746,Hazrat Ummey Al Fazal ney Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko pegham bheja aur matkey ki nabeez key barey mein puchha to unhoney isey apney betey Nazar key barey mein bayan farmaya ke wo matkey mein nabeez banata hai. subah nabeez banata hai to Sham ko pi leta hai.
5747,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab key barey mein riwayat hai ke wo is baat ko napasand farmatey they ke sabiqa nabeez ki talchat ko naee nabeez mein shamil kiya jaey taake is mein tezi paida ho.
5748,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ney farmaya : nabeez mein talchat shamil ki jaey to wo sharab ban jati hai.
5749,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ney farmaya : sharab ko sharab isliye kaha jata hai ke usey rakha jata hai. yahan tak ke jab saaf saaf (joos) khatam ho jata hai aur nichey mail kuchail aur talchat baqi reh jati hai (to usey istimal kiya jata hai (is liye) wo har us nabeez ko napasand farmatey they jis mein talchat shamil ki jaey.
5750,Hazrat Ibrahim (Nakhai) ney farmaya : salaf ka maslak ye tha ke jo koi mashrub piye aur usey nasha mehsus ho to uskey liye isey dobara peena jayez nahin.
5751,Hazrat Ibrahim sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke pukhta nabeez (sheerey) main koi harj nahin.
5752,"Hazrat Abu Miskeen sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai sey puchha ke hum sharab ya tilaa ki bachi hui talchat ko ley kar usey saaf kartey hain phir is mein munaqqey bhigo kar teen din tak pada rehney detey hain, phir usey saaf kar key rakh chhodtey hain yahan tak ke wo tayyar ho jati hai, phir hum isey pi letey hain. ( kya ye durust hai? ) unhoney kaha ke makrooh aur najaaiz hai."
5753,Hazrat ibne Shabarma ney kaha : Allah Taala Hazrat Ibrahim (Nakhai) par reham farmaai ke logon ney (nasha-aawar) nabeez key barey mein sakhti ki hai magar Hazrat Ibrahim ney iskey peeney ki rukhsat di hai.
5754,"Hazart Abu-Usaama sey riwayat hai ke mainey Abdullah bin Mubarak sey suna, wo farma rahey they ke mainey Ibrahim Nakhai key ilawa kisi (sahabi ya taaba'i) sey nasha-aawar nabeez key peeney ki rukhsat (chhoot) sahih sanad key sath nahin pai."
5755,"Hazrat Abu-Usaama ney farmaya ke mainey Sham key tamam ilaqon : Misr, Yamen aur Hijaaz mein koi shakhs Hazrat Abdullah bin Mubarak sey badh kar ilm ka Talib nahin paya."
5756,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (meri walida mohtarma) Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) key paas lakdi ka eik piyala tha jis key barey mein wo farmaya karti thin ke mainey is piyaley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko har qism ka mashrub pilaya hai : pani bhi, shehad bhi, doodh bhi aur nabeez bhi."
5757,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey nabeez key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : pani pi, shehad pi, sattu pi aur doodh pi jis key sath teri parwarish hui thi. mainey dobara sawal kiya to (ghussey sey) farmaney lagey : to sharab peena chahta hai? to sharab peena chahta hai?"
5758,Hazrat (Abdullah) ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ab logon ney kaee qism key mashrub ejaad kar liye hain. main nahin janta wo kya aur kaisey hain? bees ya chaalis saal ho gaey hain ke mainey pani ya sattu key ilawa koi aur mashrub nahin piya. unhoney nabeez ka zikr nahin farmaya.
5759,"Hazrat Ubaida (salmaani) ney farmaya ke logon ney be-shumar mashrub bana liye hain. main nahin janta, wo kon kon sey aur kaisey hain? meri haalat to ye hai ke bees saal guzar chukey hain ke merey paas pani, doodh aur shehad key ilawa koi aur mashrub nahin hota."
5760,"Hazrat ibne Shabarma sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney nabeez key barey mein Kufaa walon sey farmaya ke ye aisa fitna hai jis main tumharey chhotey parwarish paatey hain aur tumharey badey isey peetey-peetey khoosat boodhey ho jatey hain. aur jab koi shaadi hoti to Hazrat Talha aur zubaida Raziallahu anhuma logon ko doodh aur shehad pilaya kartey they. Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha gaya ke aap logon ko nabeez kyon nahin pilaatey? unhoney farmaya : main pasand nahin karta ke meri wajeh sey koi musalman nashey mein aaye."
5761,Hazrat Jareer ney farmaya : Hazrat ibne Shabarma pani aur doodh key ilawa koi mashrub nahin peetey they.
